      <title>墨西哥最高法院驳回限制司法改革的请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/mexico-s-supreme-court-dismisses-bid-to-limit-judicial-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥最高法院驳回了旨在限制国会司法改革范围的裁决，缓解了人们对与总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆对峙可能引发宪法危机的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/mexico-s-supreme-court-dismisses-bid-to-limit-judicial-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:09:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主和经济是不满的美国人投票的首要问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/democracy-economy-top-issues-as-exit-poll-sees-voter-discontent</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国九个州的投票已经结束，包括关键战场乔治亚州和北卡罗来纳州，早期结果正在开始统计，全国都在关注卡玛拉·哈里斯和共和党人唐纳德·特朗普之间激烈的竞选中选民表现如何的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/democracy-economy-top-issues-as-exit-poll-sees-voter-discontent</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 22:22:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选民起诉马斯克涉嫌 100 万美元选举抽奖欺诈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/voters-sue-musk-for-fraud-over-1-million-election-sweepstakes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[报名参加伊隆·马斯克百万美元选民抽奖的选民正在起诉特斯拉公司首席执行官及其美国政治行动委员会，声称参赛者在获奖者选出方式上受到了误导。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/voters-sue-musk-for-fraud-over-1-million-election-sweepstakes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 22:00:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>福克斯及其竞争对手采用新工具改善选举之夜通话效果</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/fox-plays-it-safe-on-election-night-after-2020-call-angered-fans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[福克斯新闻 (Fox News) 正在努力避免重演 2020 年的惨剧，当时该电视台的工作人员提前预测了乔·拜登在亚利桑那州的胜选情况，并在没有让主播做好准备的情况下将该州的地图变成了蓝色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/fox-plays-it-safe-on-election-night-after-2020-call-angered-fans</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 21:43:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当你期待选举日结果时，你应该期待什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-11-05/what-to-expect-when-you-re-expecting-results-from-election-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是华盛顿版，有关首都的金钱、权力和政治的时事通讯。今天，白宫和政治记者格雷戈里·科特解释了选票计票过程以及为什么选民今晚可能无法得到选举结果。请在此处向我们的编辑发送电子邮件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-11-05/what-to-expect-when-you-re-expecting-results-from-election-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 21:33:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街期待股市在选举障碍后反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/wall-street-is-counting-on-stocks-to-rally-after-election-hurdle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越来越多的华尔街策略师预测，美国总统大选的结果将为股市在 2024 年底上涨奠定基础，而标准普尔 500 指数今年已经上涨了 21%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/wall-street-is-counting-on-stocks-to-rally-after-election-hurdle</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 21:16:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
